@startuml
title SomeTrails Log In
actor User
participant "SomeTrails"    as ST
participant "Login Form"    as LF
participant "Auth Server"   as AS
participant "User Database" as DB

User -> ST  : Navigate to SomeTrails
ST   -> LF  : Display login form
User -> LF  : Enter email and password
LF   -> AS  : Submit credentials
AS   -> DB  : Verify credentials
DB   --> AS : Credentials valid
AS   --> LF : Login success
LF   --> ST : Redirect to logged-in site
ST   --> User : Show logged-in site

note right of AS
  Invalid credentials return
  an error to the form.
end note

@enduml
